data.description: Happy New Year! Thinking of starting 2024 in a new home? Look no further than Kallison Ranch! This 2014 New Leaf home is just over 3,300sqft and offers the master bedroom & bathroom, 1/2 bath, office and laundry room downstairs and all additional bedrooms and bathrooms upstairs. The game room overlooks the living room downstairs and is centrally located between the additional 4 bedrooms. Two upstairs bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bathroom. The large backyard has a ton of potential for entertaining. You'll want to see this one!
